title: Walter Jon Williams -  Voice of the Whirlwind
description:
Written by Walter Jon Williams
Format: MP3
Bitrate: 56 Kbps
Unabridged

In the bestselling sequel to Hardwired!, Steward's memories are 15 years old because his alpha never did have a brain-scan update, and in those 15 years, the entire world has changed. "More than either Zelazny or Gibson, (Williams) is a master of the . . . essence of thrillers and novels of political intrigue"
